<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Report Confirmation - PataID</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #25AAE1, #032540); padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">PataID</h1>
        <p style="color: white; opacity: 0.8; margin: 5px 0 0;">Lost & Found ID Platform</p>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; background: #f8fafc;">
        <h2 style="color: #032540;">ID Report Received</h2>

        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for reporting a found ID card. You have successfully helped the community!</p>

        <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;"><strong>Report Number:</strong> #<%= reportNumber %>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;"><strong>ID Type:</strong>
                <%= idType %>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;"><strong>Name on ID:</strong>
                <%= fullName %>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Campus:</strong>
                <%= campus %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= reportUrl %>"
                style="background: #25AAE1; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
                View Report
            </a>
        </div>

        <p>We have notified the owner (if they are registered) or we will wait for them to search for this ID.</p>

        <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
                Please hand over the ID to the nearest security desk if you haven't already.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #032540; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;">
        <p>&copy; <%= year %> PataID. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="opacity: 0.8;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>